 want to be the last one standing at the end of the battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Annihilate the swarm of enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710460/extras/c2d6cb820a11aaac1370f117de1d0671.poster.avif?t=1774437731\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710460/extras/c2d6cb820a11aaac1370f117de1d0671.webm?t=1774437731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710460/extras/c2d6cb820a11aaac1370f117de1d0671.mp4?t=1774437731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your character outmatches the minions in the dungeon. So go ahead and rock & roll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, stay focused. If you get distracted and your character falls in battle, you will face permadeath and have to start the journey again.</p>",
